{"tid":1022685,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[洗牌王]拉莫斯故意領黃牌或遭加監","createTime":"2019-02-15T07:43:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T03:08:08.000Z","uid":31626,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"36eede992bdaf43b19fdbc02696679b4ae8b1f4e","tid":1022685,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T07:43:07.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=rje4l1xmTn6y9o%2BHBfPaf7YQZcr3xUkCoBtK5HAxbhw%3D&h=3face43e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】就皇家馬德里名將沙治奧拉莫斯疑似故意在周中比賽領黃牌一事，歐洲足協已表態徹查，一旦證實，拉莫斯面臨多停賽1場的處分。<br />\n<br />\n周三歐聯16強首回合，皇家馬德里險勝阿積士2:1，守將沙治奧拉莫斯（Sergio Ramos）比賽末段技術性犯規，被罰黃牌，導致次回合坐波監，此舉被指故意。歐洲足協周四指出，已就拉莫斯的行為「展開紀律調查。」<br />\n<br />\n拉莫斯較早前被問到是否刻意領黃牌，從而在8強賽事前洗底時，打開天窗說亮話，直認是「身不由己」：「當時只是領先2:1，如果我說不是被逼犯規，我就講大話。」<br />\n<br />\n根據規定，如果歐洲足協查證後確認拉莫斯故意領黃牌，則該位代表皇馬出賽600場的西班牙悍將，會面臨多停賽1場的處分，若如此可說得不償失。"},{"pid":"3d041f33686d4fadfbd9b587fbd524be032a8767","tid":1022685,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T07:47:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"666e2ea15c22428da5ce584f7f9b9405f89f8671","tid":1022685,"uid":49270,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T07:59:16.000Z","msg":"唔畀人技術犯規<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a179ac34de88c4eeb606d8d8aae80a646e6c3b0","tid":1022685,"uid":77788,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T08:13:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8458d250b4590426b5dec7fae2e49302b5e6df9","tid":1022685,"uid":81644,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T08:15:08.000Z","msg":"阿積士咁撚勁,下場隨時主場輸波出局<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9550a62e7f8c08f1a80017fada493cd2022fa470",